songs.title: ​why me!
songs.lyrics:
[Pre-Chorus]
I made up my mind
I know I’m gonna try it (I know, I know)
I made up my mind, mind
I know that I’m gonna try it (Try, try, try)

[Chorus]
Nigga, why me, why me, why me, why me, why me? (Ayy)
Nigga, why me, why me, why me, why me, why me?

[Bridge]
I’m over the sorrow, I’m over today, yeah

[Pre-Chorus]
I made up my mind
I know I’m gonna try it (I know, I know)
I made up my mind- mind
I know that I’m gonna try (Try, try, try)

[Chorus]
Why me, why me, why me, why me, why me? (Oh)
Nigga, why me, why me, why me, why me, why me?
